AB  - Along with the gradual understanding of environment protection and sustainable development, government pays attention to the issue of carbon emission. In order to reduce the negative effect of carbon emission in production process on the environment, the government, as a social subject, grants rewards and punishments based on the manufacturers’ carbon emission. The government presents a carbon cap. If the manufacturers’ carbon emission in production is higher than the limit, the government will inflict punishments. On the contrary, if the emission is below this value the incentives were given to motivate the manufacturers′ enthusiasm for reducing the carbon emission. Meanwhile, an enterprise effectively reduces the cost of product by processing and manufacturing waste products in the closed-loop supply chain. Simultaneously, the recycling reduces the pollution to the environment and cuts down the resource consumption which is in accord with the social circumstance protection concept. Consequently, the closed-loop supply chain has received extensive attention of academia. Moreover, this paper considers the limited level of remanufacturing and the cognitive bias of consumers. The unit wholesale price and sales price of reengineering product are lower than the new ones. Thus, the differential pricing has theoretical value and practical significance. The coordination of differential price between new and remanufacturing products’ closed-loop supply chains was studied. Meanwhile, the rewards and punishments on manufacturers′ carbon emission was considered. A coordinate model of differential price closed-loop supply chain was constructed to discuss the selling price of products. An improved revenue sharing contract based on order quantity aims to realize supply chain coordination. By studying the results of centralized, decentralized, and the decentralized models, this paper introduces the improved revenue sharing contract, and combines with the case analysis. The following conclusions were obtained: (1) The improved revenue sharing contract can coordinate the decentralized decision closed-loop supply chain effectively. The introduction of the contract not only increases the quantity of the contract in the decentralized decision model but also cuts down the price, which makes the profit of the supply chain run up to the centralized decision level. (2) In the process of coordinating the supply chain by introducing improved revenue sharing contract, manufacturers and retailers can determine the profit distribution of supply chains by adjusting the parameters. With the increasing of contract parameters in this model, the manufacturer′s profit is decreasing, while the profit of retailer is increasing accordingly. At the same time the scope of parameters was given, in which the coordination of supply chain was achieved, and the manufacturers and retailers were willing to accept the contract. (3) Carbon emission in the production of manufacturer was cut down by implementing the rewards and punishments of government. (4) The profit of supply chain has been reduced after the change trend increases along with the aggrandizing of rewards and punishments of government. (5) When rewards and punishments strength is greater than a certain value, the policy of government can not only reduce carbon emission in the production process but also raise the profit of the supply chain. The government can increase the benefit of environment and ensure economic benefits of the supply chain members by setting reasonable rewards and punishments. © 2019,Journal of Industrial Engineering and Engineering Management. All Rights Reserved.
