st-CCS periods by 4%. For the Euro IV petrol car NOX emissions also increased by 6% between pre- and post-CCS periods. These findings will help to further understand the extent to which congestion charging reduces vehicle emissions in London. © 2005 Elsevier Ltd. All rights reserved.
